{{DISPLAYTITLE:List of ''The Boondocks'' episodes}} {{Cleanup|date=August 2010}} <!-- episode descriptions are ADVERT teasers, not encyclopedic summaries -->
The following is a '''list of episodes''' for the [[Adult Swim]] [[animated television series]] ''[[The Boondocks (TV series)|The Boondocks]]''. Created as a derivative of the [[The Boondocks (comic strip)|comic strip]] from which it originated, the series premiered on November 6, 2005 after receiving generally positive reviews from national critics. 45 episodes have been produced over three seasons.<ref name="Metacritic.com">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/shows/boondocks|title=Metacritic.com composite score for ''The Boondocks'' Season 1}}</ref> In 2011 it was announced that ''The Boondocks'' has been renewed for a fourth season, which will consist of 20 episodes.<ref name=interview>[http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pjSrTvd94TU John Witherspoon interview]</ref>
